mitgutsch-fight.jpg.description: A man in a blue suit is waving a small white flag. He is standing on a green ledge on the left side of the image, near the top. He is facing right.

whodoeswhat-city.jpg.description: A dark brown cello is leaning against the front of the light green house, near the lower left corner. Its neck is pointing towards the top left.

whodoeswhat-city2.jpg.description: A man in a black suit is playing a saxophone in the lower center of the image. He is standing on a grassy area just below a playground.

whodoeswhat-city3.jpg.description: A small yellow electrical box is located near the bottom right corner of the image. It's below a temporary orange building, to the left of a forklift carrying boxes, and just above some PVC pipes.  It has a small black symbol on it.

A small, yellow electrical box is visible on the bottom right side of the image.  It's mounted on the orange portable building, just left of a stack of pipes. To its right is a small white car, a forklift, and a dump truck with an excavator on its trailer.

The yellow electrical box is located to the right of the temporary office building, among the construction supplies, next to some grey pipes. It has a square grey door with a black handle. It is sitting on a small concrete slab.

The small, rectangular, yellow electrical box is on the ground in front of and to the left of the orange trailer, below and left of the yellow dumper truck, and just to the right of some pipes sticking out of the ground. It is facing left and has some unreadable text written on it in black. There appear to be wires going in and out of it.

The yellow electrical box is mounted to the side of the orange portacabin building, which is located in the bottom right of the image. It is below and to the left of where a worker is waving from the cab of a yellow and gray dump truck. It is in front of some drain pipes, and next to a small white three-wheeled car.

It's situated near some orange construction trailers and pipes, slightly below and to the left of a white microcar.  It appears to be connected to the trailers by a wire.  There are some illegible labels on its surface.

The small yellow electrical box is located at the bottom of the image, slightly right of center.  It is mounted on the side of an orange portacabin/office next to some stacked pipes.  A small white car is parked in front of it.

The small, rectangular, yellow electrical box is located near the bottom right of the image. It is attached to the side of an orange shipping container that has some windows. Several sections of piping lie next to the electrical box and shipping container. A small white car is parked next to it as well.
The small yellow electrical box is on the bottom right, slightly left of center. It is below an orange container building and left of some stacked bricks. It has a black danger symbol on it.

The small yellow electrical box is attached to the orange construction trailer in the lower right area of the image. It has a black keypad and wires running from it. There are concrete pipes next to the box and a small white car parked facing it.

The small, rectangular, yellow electrical box is on the ground, to the left of the orange construction trailer and partially obscured by some grey pipes.  It has some small black markings/text on the front of it.

The small, rectangular, yellow electrical box is on the right side of the image, slightly below the center. It is mounted on the outside wall of the orange construction trailer.  A black electrical cable extends down from the box into the ground.

The small, rectangular, yellow electrical box is on the ground to the left of the orange construction trailer. It is beneath and between some grey piping. There are black lines and a small grey box attached to it.

The small, yellow electrical box is on the right side of the image, near the bottom. It is attached to an orange portacabin and is very close to some drainage pipes. It is below a small white car and partially obscured by dirt and rubble.
The yellow electrical box is attached to the orange construction trailer. It is beneath the trailer’s window and positioned to the left of some grey pipes.

The small yellow electrical box is on the right side of the image, mounted on the side of the orange construction trailer. It's below and to the left of a stack of bricks and other construction supplies. It's very small compared to the other objects around it, almost square, and seems to have some wires or markings on it.
The firetruck is in the center-left of the image, in front of the fire station. It is primarily red and has a ladder extended. Firefighters are gathered around it, some holding equipment.
The small yellow electrical box is located near the bottom right corner of the image, in front of the orange construction trailer.

The small yellow electrical box is located near the bottom of the image, slightly right of center.  It sits on the ground in front of an orange portacabin and beside some construction supplies like pipes and bricks.

river-adventure-house.jpg.description: A large, inflatable blue whale is attached to the top of a yellow waterslide near the upper-left of the image. Its underside appears white and it is positioned horizontally, facing toward the right.

A large, inflatable blue whale is located in the top left corner of the image. It appears to be attached to a yellow, spiral waterslide that leads down to a swimming pool. The whale seems to be suspended in the air and functions as a decorative element at the top of the slide.
